column5: The MNR on line deer survey has a glitch. They are working on it as I type. Should be back up in a couple days.Fixed, I just did mine. http://www.mnr.gov.on.ca/en/Business/FW/1C...age/278518.html
Is this the same survey that I get in the mail?  ... what you shot...when...where...etc
can u post a link i cant seem to find it, i hope there is also the moose and bear survey
I got mine in the mail today.The tears are making it hard to read.  I,ll fill it out tonight and drop it of in the mail.
Is it just for the controlled hunt?
I noticed this morning filling it out,it is for all deer hunting.So wait til the dec15 Doug.
This is for controlled Deer hunt. The rest, I'm not sure. http://www.mnr.gov.on.ca/en/Business/FW/1C...age/278518.html
